    "description": "Witchhazel Woods is a story-heavy adventure game where you play as Dylan, a teenage girl on a mission to rescue her dog, Georgia. Georgia goes missing during a game of fetch, leaving you alone in the woods with nothing but the twig you had thrown for her.<br><br>As you journey deeper into the woods, you'll meet an array of animals and...creatures. Every critter has their own story and predicament. Can you find a creature who might have a use for your twig? If so, they might be willing to trade with you for something better.<br><br>By making the right series of trades, you can help many of the woods' creatures, and find the key to getting Georgia back in the process.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><br>- 17 tradable characters<br>- A branching narrative<br>- Funny and emotive dialogue with choices that matter<br>- A mixture of hand-drawn pixel art and procedurally generated elements<br>- Original soundtrack<br>- And to answer the all-important question: yes, you can pet the dog.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833560/extras/dca6c51d3b48daf7e831c0aff1e83b19.poster.avif?t=1730586564\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833560/extras/dca6c51d3b48daf7e831c0aff1e83b19.webm?t=1730586564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833560/extras/dca6c51d3b48daf7e831c0aff1e83b19.mp4?t=1730586564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
